description: On this episode of The CouRage and Nadeshot Show, CouRage and Nadeshot welcome on streamer and YouTuber, Pokimane. They discuss the Faze H1ghSky1 Twitch ban controversy, Pokimane's first time at EDC, choose who they would save in a battle royale, and more!
